sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant B as 🖥️ Browser
    participant F as ⚙️ Flask App
    participant DB as 💾 SQLite Database

    U->>B: Enter email and password
    B->>F: POST /admin_login (AJAX)
    activate F
    F->>DB: Query User by email
    activate DB
    DB-->>F: Return user record
    deactivate DB
    F->>F: Verify password (bcrypt/werkzeug)
    alt ✅ Password Valid
        F->>F: Create session (user_id, role, name)
        F-->>B: JSON {success: true, role: "teacher"}
        B->>B: Redirect to role-specific dashboard
    else ❌ Password Invalid
        F-->>B: JSON {success: false, message: "Invalid credentials"}
        B-->>U: Display error message
    end
    deactivate F
